    <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--padding">
  Make an FOI request
</h2>

    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            Read about the Freedom of Information (FOI) Act and <a href="https://www.gov.uk/make-a-freedom-of-information-request/the-freedom-of-information-act" class="govuk-link brand__color">how to make a request</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            Check <a href="/government/publications?departments[]=hm-revenue-customs&amp;publication_type=foi-releases" class="govuk-link brand__color">our previous releases</a> to see if we’ve already answered your question.
          </li>
            <li>Make a new request by contacting us using the details below.</li>
        </ol>

</div>

        <div class="organisation__contact-section " lang="en">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading govuk-heading-s gem-c-heading--padding">
